text: Missen may refer to: == Surname == *Alan Missen (1925–1986), Australian politician *Edward Missen (1875–1927), English cricketer *François Missen (born 1933), French journalist == Places == *Missen-Wilhams, is a municipality in the district of Oberallgäu in Bavaria *Missen Ridge, is a long, ice-covered ridge situated south of Davis Ice Piedmont, on the north coast of Victoria Land, Antarctica
